LORE kiess-merchant
FLAGS KIESS MERCHANT
- Trade Syndics coordinate all caravan contracts along Roc Road; their annex
  manages all commercial flow between Midgaard and the western frontier
- Evermeet's collapse disrupted trade credit chains; Kiess rebuilt on
  cash-basis; most transactions are pay-now; credit requires Trade Syndic
  co-signature
- Tariff-sharing negotiations with Kowloon ongoing; check Syndics' current
  posted schedule before quoting eastern route prices
- Serathi sky-road corridors: Syndics negotiating access to pre-Evermeet
  roost-chronicles, which have route intelligence value
- Forest products (herbs, rare timber, relic fragments) from forest routes
  have seasonal availability tied to expedition success; inventory accordingly
- White civic stone, blue-and-gold banners, prismatic glasswork identify
  Kiess-certified buildings; look for the Syndic stamp on trade stalls
~
